(12, 71, '50-maternity-outfits-at-all-price-points.jpeg', '89', '50 Maternity Outfits At All Price Points', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">I have been getting a lot of questions about maternity outfits &ndash; since the bulk of my pregnancy was Spring/Summer I thought it was perfect timing to share a recap of some of my outfits from my pregnancy last year! I compiled a bunch of outfits of what I wore all into one post, so make sure you pin to save for future reference!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">During my pregnancy, I was all about keeping it cool and comfortable. While I did buy a lot of new pieces for this pregnancy, less than 10% of them were actually maternity pieces! I bought a ton of affordable basics and just sized up to make some room for the bump. I&rsquo;m typically a size S, so by the middle of my pregnancy I was sizing up to a M and by the end I was sometimes sizing up to a L. As you are about to see, dresses became my best friend! If I could tell you to get any one staple it&rsquo;s a bodycon dress. I loved the ones from Forever21&nbsp;&ndash; they are super cheap but probably my most worn. I got a medium and it lasted my whole pregnancy because they are super stretchy! They are a miracle worker when it comes to maternity style. Keep scrolling for some maternity style inspo, from dressy to casual:</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">DRESSES</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_5710-1.jpeg\" style=\"height:1818px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">This first dress is show below at all trimesters of my pregnancy. The same dress&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-09-at-11.43.06-AM.png\" style=\"height:1114px; width:884px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy travel style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.22.37-AM.png\" style=\"height:1478px; width:1186px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\"chic pregnancy outfit ideas\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.19.49-AM-e1570548423609.png\" style=\"height:1372px; width:1094px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"who what wear\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_6754-e1557715429701.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity blogger\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_7815-1.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity style ideas\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_9889-e1558620108645.jpeg\" style=\"height:1964px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"casual pregnancy style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.23.44-AM.png\" style=\"height:1422px; width:1134px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity style inspo\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0936-1.jpg\" style=\"height:2040px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity style guide\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Photo-Jun-11-5-01-09-PM.jpg\" style=\"height:2060px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity dresses\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Photo-Aug-08-3-11-56-PM-e1565619165315.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity fashion\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Photo-Jul-08-3-25-28-PM-e1562908287936.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"affordable pregnancy style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Photo-Aug-22-9-14-34-PM-1-e1566570603385.jpg\" style=\"height:1744px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"cute pregnancy fashion\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Photo-Aug-26-5-15-26-PM.jpg\" style=\"height:1846px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy sweater dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Photo-Sep-16-1-28-37-PM.jpg\" style=\"height:1920px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy office style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/whitebodycondress.jpg\" style=\"height:1935px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_6475-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"affordable pregnancy outfits\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.23.24-AM.png\" style=\"height:1504px; width:1102px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy street style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/f4b17d22-72b4-11e9-9fed-0242ac110002.jpg\" style=\"height:1012px; width:810px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"cute pregnancy dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.22.52-AM.png\" style=\"height:1260px; width:970px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"dressy pregnancy style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.20.57-AM.png\" style=\"height:1422px; width:1138px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"yellow pregnancy maxi dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.20.24-AM.png\" style=\"height:1466px; width:1174px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">SHORTS/PANTS:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_6616-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"dressy pregnancy style with blazer\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/bikershorts-and-blazer-outfit.jpg\" style=\"height:2022px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"sophisticated maternity wear\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-11.19.03-AM-1-e1570552312809.png\" style=\"height:1451px; width:1126px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/A123-1.jpg\" style=\"height:1208px; width:1137px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-09-at-12.31.39-PM.png\" style=\"height:1404px; width:1034px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-09-at-11.47.26-AM.png\" style=\"height:1330px; width:918px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_7992.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_9364.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">SKIRTS</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy outfit ideas\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG_8073-e1568043644189.jpg\" style=\"height:1772px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Skirts can work just as well post-pregnancy as during &ndash; the key is finding a flowy skirt with a stretchy waist band! So easy to dress up or down to make work for any occasion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"office maternity style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Photo-Aug-06-3-13-03-PM.jpg\" style=\"height:2131px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"leopard maternity pieces\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IMG_2409-e1565367035443.jpeg\" style=\"height:1816px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_6580-scaled.jpeg\" style=\"height:2560px; width:1920px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_9743-rotated.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"fall maternity style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-08-at-12.08.31-PM.png\" style=\"height:1350px; width:1090px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">ROMPERS:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_2877-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Rompers are a great option for maternity wear! They usually have a little bit of give around the waist &ndash; just size up one and you can usually make it work well into your second trimester, and also you&rsquo;ll be glad to have some cute romper options post-pregnancy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_2235-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">SPORTSWEAR/LOUNGE:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity travel style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IMG_1756-e1565193372744.jpg\" style=\"height:1699px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity loungewear\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Photo-Jul-28-4-44-20-PM-scaled-e1586445693681.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_6886-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_7206.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_9984.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_9303-rotated.jpeg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/36AD64C0-7E0A-4AC9-AAE1-11EA1DB8F799.jpeg\" style=\"height:2418px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">BABY SHOWER INSPO:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"white maxi pregnancy dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/DG8A0657.jpg\" style=\"height:1904px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"pregnancy dressy style\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Photo-Aug-10-10-04-38-AM-3-e1565835564815.jpg\" style=\"height:1700px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"formal dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_7184-1.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"grey formal dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_7443-1.jpeg\" style=\"height:1857px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"maternity cocktail dress\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Photo-Aug-10-9-27-24-PM-e1565670076380.jpg\" style=\"height:1700px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JPf0hq\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MATERNITY.jpg\" style=\"height:2131px; width:1360px\" /></a></p>\r\n', 0, 'XX, Christine', '2021-06-25 18:52:40', 0, 0),
(13, 71, 'what-to-pack-for-your-beach-vacay.png', '90', 'What To Pack For Your Beach Vacay', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We&rsquo;re headed to Florida tomorrow! The beach is always our first choice for any vacation, so I&rsquo;m looking forward to soaking up every second of sun and time together.&nbsp; I love buying some new swimsuits or accessories for our trips but I feel like I hit the jackpot on Amazon beach finds &ndash; almost everything was under $50.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sharing some of my favorites from my try-on haul that I&rsquo;m packing for our trip below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"beach, summer, vacay, amazon \" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-22-54-PM-2-scaled-e1622754917592.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer, beach, vacay, amazon \" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-14-55-PM-scaled-e1622747893173.jpg\" style=\"height:1700px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">I love this brown two piece from Amazon for a neutral beach-ready look. I ordered it in the blue too and loved it so much I had to get it in this pretty brown. It&rsquo;s super flattering and looks 10x more expensive than it is. I&rsquo;ve been loving the pretty linen button-down look as an easy coverup and found this one in multiple colors &ndash; it&rsquo;s a super easy piece you can just throw on for the day as a beach cover up or with denim cut-offs for a day out. For accessories I&rsquo;m obsessed with this hat! I don&rsquo;t have anything in this color tone and the cord detail is so good. Also found this one that is under $25. Hats are a must for any beach getaway! also love these colorful rings and beaded chokers to bring in more color.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-39-53-PM-scaled-e1622754809586.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">This multi-color cream two-piece is under $25 and such a good fit! It&rsquo;s super comfortable and good coverage so it&rsquo;s functional too (a must with kids!) Love the color palette too. Also got this black &amp; white floral bag &ndash; it&rsquo;s one of those things Tiktok made me buy and I was still a little skeptical until I got it in person and now I&rsquo;m obsessed. It&rsquo;s a fun statement accessory and perfect to take down to the pool or beach if you&rsquo;re packing light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-50-18-PM-scaled-e1623251633724.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-50-04-PM-scaled-e1623251696596.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">These shorts are such a steal! They are under $25 and are a super lightweight material that&rsquo;s perfect for surviving the summer heat. I got them in a size S and M and they both fit but I liked the looser fit of the medium. So I would size up if you&rsquo;re in between sizes. I paired them with this knit tank which is another one of my favorite finds. It&rsquo;s super versatile and so easy to style (also under $20!).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-45-53-PM-scaled-e1623251746185.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-44-03-PM-scaled-e1623251771988.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">This black dress is probably the biggest silhouette of the season. So sleek and sophisticated but the flirty cut-outs make it perfect for summer. It&rsquo;s under $25 and comes in multiple colors &ndash; love this look for a night out or romantic dinner on the beach! So good with this brown ribbed clutch and gold-chain sandals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-01-56-PM-scaled-e1623252007685.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-02-02-PM-scaled-e1623252026919.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">I shared this black set&nbsp;the other day and it&rsquo;s selling fast. It it&rsquo;s the easiest summer outfit but also super versatile since you can mix and match with other pieces. Love the ruffled detail on the top and the slit on the pants makes it feel like such a statement piece. Ordered in both blue and white. Huge steal under $40 for the set!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-59-34-PM-scaled-e1623251900119.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-55-23-PM-scaled-e1623251875442.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Here&rsquo;s an example of mixing and matching the bottoms from this set. One of the reasons I love neutrals so much is you can combine them for endless outfits &ndash; a must when you&rsquo;re traveling! Love the lightweight trousers with this pretty knit crop &ndash; just add a sun dat to keep it feeling summery for an easy daytime look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Sharing a few more of my favorite neutral beach-finds below!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Amazon-Templates-26-1-e1622763479332.png\" style=\"height:1423px; width:1241px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Ok moving on to my colorful beach finds!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-32-26-PM-scaled-e1623252138357.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-3-30-45-PM-scaled-e1623252159849.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Love the strap detail onthis tie-dye bikini! I&rsquo;m wearing it in a medium &ndash; it definitely runs a little small so if you are in between sizes I would recommend sizing up. (I could&rsquo;ve even sized up to a large in the top.) It&rsquo;s pretty cheeky as far as swimsuit bottoms go but the print is so good! Such a fun suit for summer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-22-11-PM-scaled-e1623252181908.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-17-25-PM-scaled-e1623252206982.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Another colorful bikini I couldn&rsquo;t resist. This one comes with this pretty scarf to wrap as a bottom. It&rsquo;s a great cover up and I love all the bold colors together! Ordered it in a few different colors and similar set with longer wrap skirts, but this one was by far my fave. Obsessed!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-29-36-PM-scaled-e1623252256352.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-29-48-PM-scaled-e1623252279576.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Any romper this cute for under $50 is a huge win in my book. Love the full silhouette so it reads like a dress but the shorts make it functional enough to be able to wear out and about without having to worry about keeping things covered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-56-50-PM-scaled-e1623252430314.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Photo-May-24-4-54-57-PM-scaled-e1623252407152.jpg\" style=\"height:1813px; width:1360px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">I saw someone where an oversized linen button up over a biker shorts set and I was instantly in love! The linen button up is the perfect way to dress up your biker shorts set to make it a little more put together and sophisticated. And how good is this shade of orange!! So pretty! It comes in 7 colors. Also love it with this cute ribbed clutch to take it from gym ready to brunch ready.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Linking more of my favorite colorful beach finds below!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"summer beach vacay\" src=\"https://www.hellofashionblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Amazon-Templates-24-1-e1622757845825.png\" style=\"height:1470px; width:1215px\" /></p>\r\n', 1, 'Do Ba Truong', '2021-06-26 11:55:05', 14, 0);

