nd follow the prompts.</p>\r\n', 0, 3.6, '2021-06-21 08:29:44'),
(22, 3, 'Saint Laurent Cassandra Sandals', 'saint-laurent-cassandra-sandals.jpeg', 'saint-laurent-cassandra-sandals-sub-1.jpeg, saint-laurent-cassandra-sandals-sub-2.jpeg, saint-laurent-cassandra-sandals-sub-3.jpeg, saint-laurent-cassandra-sandals-sub-4.jpeg', '#000000', '35, 36, 38', '29', 1295, 56, 0, '<p>Enter content under section corresponding, does not remove or change section default, please!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>1. Information:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Must-have of Saint Laurent collections, Cassandra sandals are proposed for S/S 2020 in a new and bright version in black patent leather. The monogram covered by tone on tone rhinestones sits between the thin straps wrapping the foot, slender by the 110 stiletto heel, partly balanced by the platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Adjustable ankle strap</li>\r\n	<li>Round open toe</li>\r\n	<li>Monogram covered&nbsp;by rhinestones</li>\r\n	<li>Stiletto heel, platform</li>\r\n	<li>Black colour</li>\r\n	<li>100% Calfskin</li>\r\n	<li>Heel 110 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Made&nbsp;in Italy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. Details and Care:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;100% Calfskin Leather. Made in Italy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>3. Shipping and Returns:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Our customers can track their shipments using the DHL or UPS tracking service.<br />\r\nThe Customer will receive a merchandise shipment confirmation by SMS and email with a DHL or UPS Tracking Number that can be used to check the shipment status at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Michele Franzese Moda wishes to ensure complete satisfaction to their customers also by offering the opportunity to return one or more ordered items and receive a refund equal to the price of the returned items. The return of the goods are at the expense and under the responsibility of the Customer that will need to act and send an email return request within 72 working hours after delivery date and then only if the goods meet all the &ldquo;conditions of return&rdquo; listed below